def get_ans(x1,y1,x2,y2):
    def_x = abs(x2-x1)
    def_y = abs(y2-y1)

    if x2 < x1 and y2 <= y1:
        x3 = x2+def_y
        y3 = y2-def_x
        x4 = x1+def_y
        y4 = y1-def_x 
    elif y2 < y1 and x1 <= x2:
        x3 = x2+def_y
        y3 = y2+def_x
        x4 = x1+def_y
        y4 = y1+def_x     
    elif x2 > x1 and y1 <= y2:
        x3 = x2-def_y
        y3 = y2+def_x
        x4 = x1-def_y
        y4 = y1+def_x 
    elif y2 > y1 and x1 >= x2:
        x3 = x2-def_y
        y3 = y2-def_x
        x4 = x1-def_y
        y4 = y1-def_x

    print(x3,y3,x4,y4)
    #return x3,y3,x4,y4
